否则的话我们没办法搬救兵！
Somebody's got to go,
or we don't get help!

860
00:46:02,208 --> 00:46:03,875
拜托 我们快离开这里吧
Please,
let's get out of here!

861
00:46:03,875 --> 00:46:05,583
你们自己保重
Watch out for yourselves.

862
00:46:07,500 --> 00:46:09,875
到电话那里去 在那呆着
Go over by the phone.
Stay there.

863
00:46:09,875 --> 00:46:11,208
如果电话响了 喊我
If it rings, call me.

864
00:46:50,750 --> 00:46:51,916
你好
Hello.

865
00:46:51,916 --> 00:46:53,375
本耐尔大夫在吗？
Is Dr. Bennell there?

866
00:46:53,375 --> 00:46:55,583
- 在 我去叫他
- 不要紧
- Yes. I'll get him.
- Never mind.

867
00:46:55,583 --> 00:46:57,875
请转告他萨克拉门托那边
仍然线路忙就可以了...
Just tell him the Sacramento
circuits are still busy...

868
00:46:57,875 --> 00:46:59,583
再问问他是否需要我继续尝试帮他转接
and ask him if he wants me
to keep trying.

869
00:46:59,583 --> 00:47:00,916
好的 稍等
All right. Hold on.

870
00:47:00,916 --> 00:47:03,041
米尔斯 那边还是线路忙！
Miles,
the circuits are still busy!

871
00:47:03,041 --> 00:47:04,416
让她继续试！
Tell her to keep trying!

872
00:47:04,416 --> 00:47:06,583
还有 再试试三藩市和华盛顿！
Also, try San Francisco
and Washington!

873
00:47:12,875 --> 00:47:14,375
我们现在立即走人
We're getting
out of here right now.

874
00:47:14,375 --> 00:47:15,583
去哪里？
Where are we going?

875
00:47:15,583 --> 00:47:16,750
莎莉家
Sally's!

876
00:47:19,291 --> 00:47:21,250
洛杉矶方面还是接不通
We're still unable
to get through to Los Angeles.

877
00:47:21,250 --> 00:47:23,625
需要我继续尝试吗？
Do you wish me to keep trying?

878
00:47:23,625 --> 00:47:24,916
本耐尔大夫？
Dr. Bennell?

879
00:47:26,125 --> 00:47:27,791
本耐尔大夫？
Dr. Bennell?

880
00:47:27,791 --> 00:47:29,625
我需要个可以信任的人...
I needed
someone I could trust...

881
00:47:29,625 --> 00:47:32,750
然后我发现莎莉
我的护士 是最好的人选
and I figured Sally, my nurse,
was my best bet.

882
00:47:32,750 --> 00:47:35,916
我决定试试给她打电话看看她是否在家
I decided to try to phone her
to see if she was at home.

883
00:47:35,916 --> 00:47:37,916
也许公用付费电话线路还没有被占领
Maybe they hadn't
taken over the pay phones.

884
00:47:37,916 --> 00:47:40,166
我试试付费电话
I'll try the pay phone.

885
00:47:40,166 --> 00:47:42,166
嗨 麦克！
Hey, Mac!

886
00:47:42,166 --> 00:47:43,958
哦 嗨 大夫 你好吗？
Oh, hi, doc.
How are you?

887
00:47:43,958 --> 00:47:46,625
听着 可以赶快帮我加个几加仑吗？
我赶时间
Will you get me
a couple gallons fast?

888
00:47:46,625 --> 00:47:48,791
当然
玛莎 大夫在赶时间
Sure.
Martha, doc's in a hurry!

889
00:47:48,791 --> 00:47:50,125
你负责刷挡风玻璃 好吗？
Get the windshield, will you?

890
00:47:53,333 --> 00:47:56,333
我得把钥匙拔下来去开油箱
I have to have the keys
to open the gas tank.

891
00:47:58,625 --> 00:48:01,083
这条路那边有病人？
Somebody sick out this way?

892
00:48:01,083 --> 00:48:02,916
那边出了事故
There's been an accident.

893
00:48:02,916 --> 00:48:05,041
有意思 我们还没听到这个消息
Funny.
We haven't heard about it.

894
00:48:05,041 --> 00:48:06,708
呃 刚刚才发生的事情
It just happened.

895
00:48:06,708 --> 00:48:09,166
我还没来得及拨她的号码...
Before I could
even get her number...

896
00:48:09,166 --> 00:48:11,250
就看见麦克靠近了我的车的后备箱
I saw Mac closing
the trunk of my car.

897
00:48:11,250 --> 00:48:12,541
他或许是在帮我检查备胎情况...
He could have been
checking my spare tire...

898
00:48:12,541 --> 00:48:14,166
但我不这么想
but I didn't think so.

899
00:48:14,166 --> 00:48:15,333
这样就好了
That should do it.

900
00:48:15,333 --> 00:48:16,541
谢谢你
Thank you.

901
00:48:16,541 --> 00:48:17,750
都搞定了？
All set?

902
00:48:17,750 --> 00:48:19,291
