- 好的 多谢
- All set, doc.
- Fine. Thanks.

903
00:48:19,291 --> 00:48:21,791
- 记我账上 好吗？
- 当然了 大夫
- Put it on my bill, will you?
- Sure, doc.

904
00:48:41,375 --> 00:48:43,291
怎么了？
What's the matter?

905
00:49:09,250 --> 00:49:11,666
我们得现在赶去莎莉家
We've got to make it
to Sally's house.

906
00:49:21,458 --> 00:49:24,333
我不确定是否再有任何人可以信任了...
I wasn't sure
I could trust anyone...

907
00:49:24,333 --> 00:49:26,833
但无论怎样 我想去莎莉那里碰碰运气
but I took a chance
and drove to Sally's anyway.

908
00:49:33,041 --> 00:49:35,750
当我看到屋子前面停了很多车时...
When I saw several cars
in front of the house...

909
00:49:35,750 --> 00:49:37,291
我决定谨慎点
I decided to play it safe.

910
00:49:43,208 --> 00:49:44,500
有什么不对吗？
What's wrong?

911
00:49:44,583 --> 00:49:47,750
也许没有 但还是先不要进去...
直到我确定那边安全为止
Probably nothing,but we're not going 
in there until I'm sure it's safe.

912
00:49:47,750 --> 00:49:49,916
握紧方向盘
随时准备立刻开车...
Slide under the wheel
and get out of here fast...

913
00:49:49,916 --> 00:49:52,250
如果有任何人出现来抓我们的话
if anybody shows up
looking for us.

914
00:50:19,416 --> 00:50:21,083
宝宝睡着了吗 莎莉？
The baby asleep yet, Sally?

915
00:50:21,083 --> 00:50:23,041
还没呢
不过就快了...
Not yet,
but she will be soon...

916
00:50:23,041 --> 00:50:25,250
然后就再也不会哭闹了
and there'll be no more tears.

917
00:50:25,250 --> 00:50:27,083
需要我把这个放在她的房间吗？
Shall I put this in her room?

918
00:50:27,083 --> 00:50:28,750
是的 放在她的围床上
Yes. In her playpen.

919
00:50:28,750 --> 00:50:31,958
不 等等
也许由我来更好
No, wait.
Maybe I'd better take it.

920
00:50:31,958 --> 00:50:33,375
怎么不进屋去呢 米尔斯？
Why don't you go in, Miles?

921
00:50:33,375 --> 00:50:35,083
我们大家都在等你呢
We've been waiting for you.

922
00:50:41,625 --> 00:50:43,791
